➜90后北京姑娘哈佛毕业后，回国造了栋美术馆，送给艺术家父母
http://www.sohu.com/a/418164749_157906	50603
<p class="ql-align-center"><iframe width="500" height="300" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" border="0" allowfullscreen="true" src="//tv.sohu.com/s/sohuplayer/iplay.html?bid=214542541&amp;vars=%5B%5B%22showRecommend%22%2C0%5D%5D&amp;disablePlaylist=true&amp;mute=1&amp;autoplay=false"></iframe></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200913/2abfb14f1e5c4af6976f88fc3673c092.jpeg" style="user-select: auto;" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>90后北京姑娘刘焉陈，</p>
<p>哈佛大学硕士毕业，</p>
<p>父母是一对艺术家，</p>
<p>2016年，她为父母在京郊顺义</p>
<p>造了一栋美术馆级别的工作室。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200913/160819d672874f1d8d29aa6d041b48c9.gif" style="user-select: auto;" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200913/7ea344096f8f43f8bb2ae67a3372332b.gif" style="user-select: auto;" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
